jekyll-latex
============

Writing posts for Jekyll in LaTeX.

Features:
- generates posts with YAML front-matter from LaTeX files (requires stringex gem)
- uses TtH (http://hutchinson.belmont.ma.us/tth/) as converter
- highlights code for \minted and \inputminted LaTeX commands
- valid minted options: linenos,firstnumber

Jekyll configuration file options:
  #directory for latex files and includes
  latex: _latex

